snippet.title: 💀 Phantasmal: Terror Evolved 💀
snippet.description:
Phantasmal is a Lovecraftian survival horror that evolves every time you play.   Set in the Kowloon Walled City, you must depend on your cunning to survive the creatures that reside there!

Steam Full Release 14th Apr PDT
Lookout for the 20% discount on launch day!

Steam Page: http://store.steampowered.com/app/342550
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Joe_Eyemobi
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Phantasmal-386577128151070/
